Package: smoothemplik
Type: Package
Title: Smoothed Empirical Likelihood
Version: 0.0.14
Authors@R: person(given=c("Andreï", "Victorovitch"), family="Kostyrka",
        role=c("aut", "cre"), email="andrei.kostyrka@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Andreï Victorovitch Kostyrka <andrei.kostyrka@gmail.com>
Description: Empirical likelihood methods for asymptotically efficient
    estimation of models based on conditional or unconditional moment
    restrictions through fast Rcpp implementations of kernel-based
    non-parametric methods for density/regression estimation and numerical
    routines for empirical likelihood maximisation.
License: EUPL
Encoding: UTF-8
